name: Found First
overview:
FoundFirst.com Strategic Tools to promote your web: Search Engine Submission and Positioning, Content Marketing, Viral Marketing, Link exchange and creative web promotion techniques. We regularly perform web ranking experiments to know which are the limits of SEO. Many websites were detected to be “over-SEO” and were penalized by G. We developed original methods to detect the limits of SEO, and to establish a “penalization index” that requires action by the webmaster, SEO or website promotion campaign director. Read about Viral Marketing, the Googleometry project and our SEO experiments

Our site diagnosis system that prevents penalization by the search engines and lets you extract the maximal potential from your website.
